== 發行 ==
電影於2016年9月9日的[[2016年多倫多國際影展|多倫多國際影展]]上舉行世界首映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2016/09/anne-hathaway-colossal-review|title=Anne Hathaway Faces a Very Modern Monster in Charming, Surprising Colossal|website=[[浮華世界_(雜誌)|Vanity Fair]]|first=Richard|last=Lawson|date=2016-09-09|accessdate=2017-01-13|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118085803/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2016/09/anne-hathaway-colossal-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不久之後，一家神祕的未命名公司獲得了電影的發行權<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/09/colossal-anne-hathaway-toronto-film-festival-mystery-chinese-buyer-1201818986/|title=Anne Hathaway Sci-Fi Pic ‘Colossal’ Sells To Mystery Chinese Buyer – Toronto|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Mike|last=Fleming Jr|date=2016-09-13|accessdate=2017-01-13|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125184308/https://deadline.com/2016/09/colossal-anne-hathaway-toronto-film-festival-mystery-chinese-buyer-1201818986/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來證實是湯姆·奎因和提姆·雷格的未命名新發行公司NEON<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thewrap.com/anne-hathaways-colossal-picked-up-by-tom-quinn-and-tim-leagues-new-distributor/|title=Anne Hathaway’s ‘Colossal’ to Be Released by Tom Quinn and Tim League’s New Distributor|website=[[The_Wrap|The Wrap]]|first=Beatrice|last=Verhoeven|date=2016-09-14|accessdate=2017-01-13|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126132952/https://www.thewrap.com/anne-hathaways-colossal-picked-up-by-tom-quinn-and-tim-leagues-new-distributor/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該片將於2017年4月7日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/01/tom-quinn-tim-league-launch-neon-distribution-company-sundance-film-festival-1201885413/|title=Tom Quinn & Tim League Launch Distribution Shingle Neon For Sundance|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Mike|last=Fleming Jr|date=2017-01-13|accessdate=2017-01-13|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111225004/https://deadline.com/2017/01/tom-quinn-tim-league-launch-neon-distribution-company-sundance-film-festival-1201885413/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

